📄 PRIVACY POLICY

Effective Date: March 27, 2026

Welcome to Resume Enhancer AI (“App”, “we”, “our”, or “us”). Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we handle your information when you use our mobile application.

1. Information We Collect
a. User-Provided Content

The App allows users to input:

Resume content
Job descriptions
Job requirements

These inputs are used only to generate AI-enhanced results.

👉 We do not permanently store your resume or job-related content unless explicitly stated (e.g., saved history feature).

b. Account Information (Optional)

If you create an account, we may collect:

Email address
Basic profile details

This is used for:

Authentication
Saving user history
Managing subscriptions
c. Subscription & Payment Data

We use RevenueCat to manage subscriptions.

Payments are processed by Google Play / Apple App Store
We do not store or have access to your payment details
d. Usage Data (Limited)

We may collect limited, non-sensitive usage data such as:

App interactions
Feature usage
Error logs

This helps us improve app performance and user experience.

2. How We Use Information

We use your data to:

Generate enhanced resumes using AI
Improve app functionality
Provide customer support
Manage subscriptions and access levels
3. Data Storage & Security
We prioritize minimal data storage
Sensitive content (like resumes) is not stored permanently by default
We implement reasonable safeguards to protect your data
4. Third-Party Services

We use trusted third-party services:

OpenAI (or AI provider) – for generating resume enhancements
Supabase (if used) – for authentication and optional data storage
RevenueCat – for subscription management
Google Play / Apple – for payment processing

These services may process data as required to deliver app functionality.

5. Data Sharing

We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal data.

We only share data with third-party providers strictly to operate the app (as described above).

6. Data Retention
User-generated content is not stored unless saved by the user
Account data is retained while your account is active
You may request deletion at any time
7. Your Rights

You have the right to:

Access your data
Request deletion
Stop using the app at any time
8. Children’s Privacy

This app is not intended for children under 13.
We do not knowingly collect data from children.

